node.text: #contestgiveaway Le Pâtissier is our PCA 2021 Exclusive release—sold only to retail attendees of the trade show earlier this month. The cigar is a 6.5” x 44 exquisite expression of CT Broadleaf wrapper that exudes richness, complexity, and balance. While Le Pâtissier won’t ship until October, here’s a chance to score a Limited Edition Le Pâtissier hat now. Just leave any comment below with the hashtag #headswillroll and tag 3 friends. Winners will be announced on this post. Good luck and thx for supporting Crowned Heads🙏🏼🙏🏼🤘🏼
